                    <p>If you are interested in group tickets (3+ participants from the same organization or company) or private instruction,
                        <a href="/#contact" data-type="page">please contact us</a>.</p>

                    <h2 class="wp-block-heading">
                        <strong>Workshops</strong>
                    </h2>

                    <p>We offer customized one-hour workshops on a number of social innovation and social impact topics. If you are interested in a workshop for your team, organization or clients,
